DialogueNode.dialogue: I . . . don't know. I can't remember . . .
I can't, either. Sometimes I get glimpses of my life.
How do I get out of here?
But . . . there's something about this place that just . . . takes it all away from you.
There's no way out. We're trapped. There's a point ahead I can't get through.
I can take you there if you like. Just . . . don't go in the water. I'll find a way to get you across.
